## Installment

```bash
$ npm i xctestwd-frameworks-93 --save
```

## Location of framework

https://unpkg.com/xctestwd-frameworks-93@latest/

## Before Deploy

```bash
$ cp -rf XCTestWD/Carthage ./
```
